msgctxt "2100"
msgid ""
"それにしても\n"
"随分丹念に痛めつけられたものだな。"
msgstr "Even so, it was hurt very carefully."

msgctxt "2149"
msgid "親っさん……　俺……"
msgstr "Parents ... I ..."

msgctxt "2170"
msgid ""
"何も言うな。\n"
"今、他の牢番に見つかったら事が台無しだ。\n"
"……今すぐ着替えて、ここを出ろ。"
msgstr ""
"Don't say anything. Now, if you find it in another prison guard, things will"
" be ruined. ...... Change your clothes now and get out of here."

msgctxt "2259"
msgid "でもどうやって。"
msgstr "But how."

msgctxt "2276"
msgid ""
"心配ない。\n"
"出口まで人払いしてある。\n"
"だが短い時間だ、急げ。"
msgstr ""
"No worries. I have paid people to the exit. But it's a short time, hurry."

msgctxt "2337"
msgid "あ、ああ……"
msgstr "Ah, ah ..."

msgctxt "2350"
msgid ""
"詳しい話はあとだ。\n"
"お前はここを出たら街で腹ごしらえでもして、\n"
"その後、“隠れ家”に来い。"
msgstr ""
"More on that later. When you leave here, you can get hungry in the city, and"
" then come to the \"hiding place\"."

msgctxt "2441"
msgid "隠れ家？"
msgstr "A hideaway?"

msgctxt "2450"
msgid ""
"フッ、忘れたのか？\n"
"ワシたちが何年も暮らした塾のことを。\n"
"江戸の１年ってな、ずいぶん長いらしい。"
msgstr ""
"Did you forget it? The cram school where the eagles lived for many years. It"
" seems that one year in Edo is quite long."

msgctxt "2547"
msgid ""
"……場所は街のヤツにでも聞け。\n"
"『牽牛子塾（ケンゴシジュク）』と聞けばわかる。"
msgstr ""
"...... Ask the guy in the city about the place. You can tell by listening to"
" \"Kengoshizuka\"."

msgctxt "2626"
msgid "分かった。"
msgstr "Do you get it."

msgctxt "3104"
msgid "東洋"
msgstr "Oriental"

msgctxt "3134"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"
